name: The Crowley Law Firm, PLLC
overview: Criminal defense cases may involve a drug charge, embezzlement, white collar or federal court. The Crowley Law Firm, PLLC, is a Seattle, WA criminal lawyer available to protect criminal defendants charged with serious allegations. Our lawyers are available schedule a free consultation regarding your case. John Crowley is experienced in federal, juvenile and criminal defense cases and can help make the difference in your case. The Crowley Law Firm is dedicated to handling cases that involve the most serious of allegations and will help to fight for your freedom.
